===Noun===
'''anemia'''
# {{pathology}} A [[medical]] [[condition]] in which the [[capacity]] of the [[blood]] to transport [[oxygen]] to the [[tissue]]s is [[reduced]], either because of too few [[red blood cell]]s, or because of too little [[haemoglobin]], resulting in pallor and fatigue.

